            <div frus:doc-dateTime-max="1948-12-31T23:59:59-05:00" frus:doc-dateTime-min="1948-01-03T10:00:00-05:00" n="718" subtype="editorial-note" type="document" xml:id="d718">
                <head>
                    <hi rend="italic">Editorial Note</hi>
                </head>
                <p>This chapter presents a selection of the most important general policy papers on
                    Germany. These papers cover the full range of major German policy issues. The
                    most important of these issues have been documented in detail in the preceding
                    chapters of this volume. An elaborate cross-reference apparatus has not been
                    included with these papers. Readers should consult the earlier chapters for
                    topics and negotiations referred to in the following pages.</p>
            </div>
        </body>
